      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "7916-7993",
      "markText": "对于私派赋税、加重火耗等收益，州县官若是不拿，知府、道台怎么拿？知府、道台不拿？督抚怎么拿？督抚不拿，朝廷中枢的大员们又怎么拿？各级官员又如何“进步”呢？",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125359&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=7916&rangeEnd=7993",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/793325b0813ab9777g019acd?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=7916&rangeEnd=7993"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125359_23_1863-1936",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "1863-1936",
      "markText": "后来看到城门外的人，烧着人骨头，煮着人肉吃，才知道之前那些消失的人，都是被吃了。而吃人的人，也免不了在几天之后脸发肿、眼睛发红，体内发出燥热而死。",
      "totalCount": 143,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125359&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=1863&rangeEnd=1936",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/793325b0813ab9777g019acd?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=1863&rangeEnd=1936"
