    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125359_24_26438-26475",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "26438-26475",
      "markText": "当然不是。这起所谓“武侯显圣”的“万盏红灯”事件，很有可能是一起集体癔症。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125359&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=26438&rangeEnd=26475",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/793325b0813ab9777g019acd?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=26438&rangeEnd=26475"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125359_27_24409-24457",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "24409-24457",
      "markText": "一个赶路生员无端被捕快打死，乾隆帝最关心的是，如果“正义”主持得太快，将来生员们会不会就难管了。",
      "totalCount": 121,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125359&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=24409&rangeEnd=24457",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/793325b0813ab9777g019acd?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=24409&rangeEnd=24457"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125359_3_670-759",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "670-759",
      "markText": "无史的第一个表征，是中国史学的好传统很早便被斩断。这类好传统包括如太史公那般挣脱权力干预，站在自主立场上撰史；包括不隐恶不虚美，以起居注与实录等档案忠实详尽地记录统治者的所作所为",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125359&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=670&rangeEnd=759",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/793325b0813ab9777g019acd?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=670&rangeEnd=759"
    },
